{"tid":687065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有相有片]【隕石襲地球】雲南黑夜瞬間照亮","createTime":"2018-06-02T01:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T02:38:21.000Z","uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"178375fe329d273eed3c9b38268e8284181d66d9","tid":687065,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:56:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180602/58267857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58267857&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=8f5f8d17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58267857&h=9ffd153a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180602/58267857</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雲南網絡昨晚熱傳一段流星劃過夜空的影片，片中所見，當時原本漆黑的天空瞬間被照亮。雲南西雙版納州地震局工作人員事後表示，晚上10時左右，在景洪市上空確實出現較亮劃痕，與地面形成約70度夾角，按照一般經驗判斷，有7成機會為隕石墜落。<br />\n<br />\n據網上影片所見，事發時漆黑的天空突然出現一道亮光，劃向地平線，形成一條長長的「尾巴」，照亮半個夜空。當光源快要接觸地面時，亮光消失了。<br />\n西雙版納州地震局工作人員指昨晚10時左右，一條較亮的光線從景洪市區天空劃過，和地面大約形成70度的夾角。「一般的煙火是不會這麼亮的，也沒有甚麼聲音，快要接觸地面的時候，亮光消失了。按照一般經驗，是隕石的可能性約70%。」去年10月4日，雲南省迪慶藏族自治州香格裡拉曾出現隕石墜落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/965578/org/7cfd0c671be6b21a30f3884e320e69aa.JPEG/4esUJI0biSUsWASkdseZS4nIBF1VOLh3XVbTWV1W01k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F965578%2Forg%2F7cfd0c671be6b21a30f3884e320e69aa.JPEG%2F4esUJI0biSUsWASkdseZS4nIBF1VOLh3XVbTWV1W01k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=01e4707b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2e4321252346ea3c45fca1e351a4c65b7f56f3c","tid":687065,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefc7aea71a4ec5417e22d595c1ce34550f5f33f","tid":687065,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"隕石墜落中國境內帶來新一批稀有金屬，中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"994cdec6998d06963e03afe54aa9e50bc6e16e21","tid":687065,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"天滅支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次實射中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}